      <title>BP南非公司与壳牌下游炼油厂资产出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/bp-southern-africa-shell-downstream-to-sell-refinery-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BP Southern Africa (Pty) Ltd. 和 Shell Downstream South Africa (Pty) Ltd. 已达成协议，将各自持有的南非最大炼油厂 50% 的资产出售给国有的 Central Energy Fund SOC Ltd.。]]></description>
